<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>325</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal Isu hehpihna chun ei uh gilo a beimang,
 Ei hung tatdawk ziekin a lopi na e;
 Kumsawt hinna lultak chuh thimnuoi a mite kawmah,
 Genzak dingin kuote a chiehdawk ding?

[V2]
 Gamtin mun tin a mite kawmah,
 Na hukdamna thu kuo a kiko pih ding?
 Kei chieh dawk ing ka Lalpa na hukdamna puong zak di'n,
 Na thagau thiengtho in ei puizel in.

[V3]
 2. Semzel ingka Lalpa di'n sepgim chuh chawlhna ahi
 Lallukhuk lopi I chan theih na dingun;
 Ma a mihangsan tamtak chiehsate kha hezingin,
 Lau loin hangtakin semzel hitiu.

[V4]
 3. Dai gam leh Arakan gam Tidim biel leh Matupi,
 Fang suoka salhvak dingin Lalpa'n ei sam;
 Aw Suohpih Lalpa chielna ngilh in kihet mawh sak kin,
 Nang leh kei hi mawhpuotu I hiu ui.

[V5]
 4. Thagau mangthai khatmai bek ka hukdawk theihna dingun,
 Na thagau thiengtho chemzam in ei thuom in,
 Thim leh gimtheihna nuoi a puidawka salhvak dingin,
 Kei uh KHANGLAI TE hi ei hun mangin.</lyrics>
<title>Gamtin Mun Tin Ah</title>
</song>